room_title: Escape room "Black Ops" by Escape the Mystery Room in Albany
room_address: 1 Crossgates Mall Rd Unit C107, Albany, NY 12203
room_description: Returning after a successful mission, your special forces team find that the base was hit with the enemy's missile and abandoned by your fellow troops. Before dislocating, they've left you an encrypted escape plan. You only have an hour before the next air raid, so you must act fast to decode the plan and head for the Evac location.
